msgid "The last usable voice package was kept because Google TTS For NVDA is still the current synthesizer."
msgstr "由于 Google TTS For NVDA 仍是当前所选的语音引擎，最后一个可用的语音包已被保留。"

msgid "Waiting for you to switch away from Google TTS For NVDA before removing the last usable voice package."
msgstr "等待您从 Google TTS For NVDA 切换离开，然后再移除最后一个可用的语音包。"

msgid "You are about to remove the last usable voice package. After it is removed, Google TTS For NVDA will not have any voices available until you download another package.\n\nPackages to remove, including dependent packages: {packages}\n\nChoose Yes to remove these packages. Choose No to keep them installed."
msgstr "您即将移除最后一个可用的语音包。移除后，在您下载另一个包之前，Google TTS For NVDA 将没有任何可用语音。\n\n待移除的包（包括依赖包）：{packages}\n\n选择“是”移除这些包。选择“否”保留它们。"

msgid "You are about to remove the last usable voice package. Google TTS For NVDA is currently selected as your synthesizer, so it needs at least one voice to keep speaking.\n\nPackages to remove, including dependent packages: {packages}\n\nChoose Yes to open Select Synthesizer and switch first. Choose No to keep this package installed."
msgstr "您即将移除最后一个可用的语音包。Google TTS For NVDA 当前被选为您的语音引擎，因此它至少需要一个语音才能继续发声。\n\n待移除的包（包括依赖包）：{packages}\n\n选择“是”以打开“选择语音引擎”并先进行切换。选择“否”以保留此包。"

msgid "Downloaded {succeeded} of {total} packages. Could not download: {failList}. First error: {reason}"
